Okay, I understand! You want a more vibrant, modern, and visually engaging design with a richer color palette, while still ensuring full compatibility with older C# web views (meaning no backdrop-filter or other advanced CSS3 features).
I've completely overhauled the styling again, introducing a fresh color scheme with more depth and contrast, refined gradients, and enhanced subtle effects to make it look more contemporary and appealing. The responsive structure using float and @media queries remains robust for compatibility.
Here is the full CSS file with the enhanced styling and responsiveness:
/* Global Styles for Body */
body {
    /* A vibrant, yet soft, blue-to-purple gradient for the background */
    background: linear-gradient(to right bottom, #e0f2f7, #e6e9f0);
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; /* Modern font stack */
    color: #2c3e50; /* Deep charcoal for primary text for better readability */
    margin: 0;
    padding: 35px; /* Increased padding for more breathing room */
    background-attachment: fixed;
    background-size: cover;
    line-height: 1.65; /* Improved line spacing for readability */
}

/* Main Container */
.passenger-container {
    max-width: 920px; /* Slightly adjusted width for better balance */
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 45px; /* More internal padding */
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98); /* Near-opaque white for a clean base */
    border-radius: 30px; /* Even softer, more modern rounded corners */
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18); /* More pronounced, softer shadow for depth */
    border: 1px solid rgba(220, 220, 220, 0.5); /* Very subtle light border */
}

/* Card Styling */
.passenger-card {
    background-color: #ffffff; /* Pure white for crispness */
    border-radius: 22px; /* Larger radius for cards for a softer look */
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Gentle shadow for depth */
    padding: 45px; /* Increased padding inside cards */
    margin-bottom: 40px; /* More space between cards */
    transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out; /* Smooth transitions */
    border: 1px solid #f0f0f0; /* Subtle border for definition */
}

.passenger-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-7px); /* More noticeable lift effect on hover */
    box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Enhanced shadow on hover */
}

/* Heading Styles */
h2.passenger-title {
